{
  "stem": "2980.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then they took to work whatever they needed-- on the railroad, on the-- on the roads, whatever they had to do heavy work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we went to work in our-- in my [NON-ENGLISH]-- in my father's shop, and-- as a mechanic, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They marched us every single day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they got us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And time got worse and worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "People were dying every single day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Then came October, [NON-ENGLISH], October 1, 1942 when they started killing-- the liquidation of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "All the towns around us were already eliminated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In our town, they started killing then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Before they are dead, dug four giant open pits.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they said that there was a, a, a brick factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They're going to make bricks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But in actuality, it turned out to be the pits to, to kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Before that, we made hiding places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "My father structured a special hiding place from a cellar under one room, then to a next, to a tunnel, into the backyard, under an apple tree.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That's where the main, main hiding place-- and another one was a double attic in the-- over the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And half of the family was into the attic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And, and half went in the underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And soon enough, we ran out of food, and water, and air, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And-- but somehow, we stayed for about seven, eight days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I found out later on that the first day, they killed 1,800 Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They took them, they got them undressed in the main synagogue, and drove them naked to the open pits, and shot them, the Germans with the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Second, they-- 800; the third, 600; and so on, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
